^^WI CHARS=8 REAL INFORM=YES
% CLEAR
% INSERT !^^WI @ 3,7 EDITBOX E6 '!
% STORE FORMAT /(F8.3)/ LENGTH 8 REAL ZFM
% INSERT !'!
% OUTPUT
^^WI CHARS=8 REAL INFORM=YES
^^WI   }
^^WI  }
^^WI  @ 1,2 GRID GRIDR NROWS=5 NCOLS=3
^^WI  {
^^WI   @ 2,2 BUTTON BOK '&Ok' DEFAULT
^^WI   @ 4,2 BUTTON BXX '&Cancel'
^^WI  }
^^WI }
^^WI SHOW
^^CR
